單變數：類別型

ggplot(data = diamonds, aes(x = color)) +
geom_bar(fill = "green", colour = "black")

單變數：連續型

ggplot(data = diamonds, aes(x = carat)) +
geom_histogram(fill = "purple", bins = 30)

雙變數：連續 vs 連續

ggplot(data = diamonds, aes(x = carat, y=price)) +
geom_smooth()
## `geom_smooth()` using method = 'gam'

雙變數：離散 vs 連續

ggplot(diamonds, aes(x=clarity, y=depth)) +
geom_boxplot()

# 從數據集獲取10000個樣本數據進行分析
set.seed(20022012)
diamond_samp <- diamonds[sample(1:length(diamonds$price), 10000), ]
ggpairs(diamond_samp,lower= list(continuous = wrap("points", shape = I('.'))),
        upper = list(combo = wrap("box", outlier.shape = I('.'))))
